<div class="row shadow-panel" style="margin-left:0px;">
	<div class="span6" style="">
		<%= image_tag e_book.image_large, :style=>"width:420px;max-height:560px;min-height:560px;height:560px;" %>
	</div>
	<div class="span6">
		<br />
		<table class="table tablex">
			<tr>
				<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;"><%=link_to "#{e_book.name}", e_book_url(e_book) %></th>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="text-align:right;width:100px;border-top-width:1px;">作者：</td>
				<td><%= e_book.author %></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="text-align:right;width:100px;">语言：</td>
				<td><%= e_book.language %></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="text-align:right;width:100px;">格式：</td>
				<td><%= e_book.format %></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="text-align:right;width:100px;">出版年份：</td>
				<td><%= e_book.publish_year %></td>
			</tr>
      <% ValueSetHeader.categories.each do |category| %>
        <% unless e_book.send(ActiveSupport::Inflector.singularize(category.name)).blank? then %>
        <tr>
          <td style="text-align:right;width:100px;"><%=category.title%>：</td>
          <td><%= e_book.send(ActiveSupport::Inflector.singularize(category.name)) %></td>
        </tr>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
			<tr>
				<td style="text-align:right;width:100px;">下载链接：</td>
				<td>
          <ul class="inline">
          <% e_book.webstorage_links.each_with_index do |link, index|%>
            <li style="padding-left:0px;">
            <%= 
              unless link.ad_link.blank? then
                link_to link.name, link.ad_link, :target=>'_blank'
              else
                link_to link.name, link.url, :target=>'_blank'
              end
            %>
            </li>
          <% end %>
          </ul>
          <div id="tip_<%=e_book.id%>">
            <pre style="font-size:12px;">下载链接带有广告，广告出现5秒钟后，点击右上角“跳过广告”按钮，即可到达下载页面。广告是支撑本站长期运行的唯一收入来源。</pre>
          </div>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
		<br />
	</div>
</div>
